<?php
function factorial($n) {
  if ($n < 0) {
    return 0;
        }

  $factorial = 1;
  for ($i = $n; $i >= 1; $i--) {
    $factorial = $factorial * $i;
        }

  return $factorial;
      }
?>

def r_palindrome?(s)
  if s.length <= 1
    true
  elsif s[0] != s[-1]
    false
  else
    r_palindrome?(s[1..-2])
  end
end

def fib(n)
   if n < 2
     n
   else
     prev, fib = 0, 1
     (n-1).times do
       prev, fib = fib, fib + prev
     end
     fib
   end
 end
